Located on [[Phyrstal Island]] in the resort [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Le Yer]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Abregado-rae/Legends|Abregado-rae]], the '''Lost Loves Casino''' was a run-down [[Gambling/Legends|gambling]] house that seemed somewhat out of place in the beautiful city. Its [[Bartender/Legends|bartender]], [[Malric Blaene]] was widely known for his gossip.

